Term: Looks like you have not scanned any QR codes yet! Please scan a QR code to see entries here
Translated Text: Looks like you have not scanned any QR codes yet! Please scan a QR code to see entries here

Term: You have disabled recording of your scan activity. If you wish to enable it, please visit Settings page to re-enable it. SEQR App will continue to work without any problem without activity recording. Click on Scan below to open camera to scan the codes
Translated Text: You have disabled recording of your scan activity. If you wish to enable it, please visit Settings page to re-enable it. SEQR App will continue to work without any problem without activity recording. Click on Scan below to open camera to scan the codes

Term: Welcome to a safe way to scan QR codes! With SEQR you can now see what is behind the QR, be informed about the security of the code, and whether it is safe or risky.
Translated Text: Welcome to a safe way to scan QR codes! With SEQR you can now see what is behind the QR, be informed about the security of the code, and whether it is safe or risky.

Term: With SEQR, you can scan and read all kinds of QR Codes. It performs several checks using information from various online sources to identify potential security risks. It enables you to make informed decisions about whether or not to trust the codes and content.
Translated Text: With SEQR, you can scan and read all kinds of QR Codes. It performs several checks using information from various online sources to identify potential security risks. It enables you to make informed decisions about whether or not to trust the codes and content.

Term: If you find a phishing web link, report it and help us make transactions safer
Translated Text: If you find a phishing web link, report it and help us make transactions safer

Term: Each time you come across an incorrectly categorized information, please report it to help more people stay safer online.
Translated Text: Each time you come across an incorrectly categorized information, please report it to help more people stay safer online.

Term: to read uploaded QR Code images
Translated Text: to read uploaded QR Code images

Term: to remind you of where a QR Code (in activity) was scanned
Translated Text: to remind you of where a QR Code (in activity) was scanned

Term: Without access to the Camera, SEQR can't scan QR Codes
Translated Text: Without access to the Camera, SEQR can't scan QR Codes

Term:
Not scanned any codes in the last 30 seconds, reopen Scan tab when you are ready to scan.

Keeping the camera on for long may drain battery.
Opening the Activity tab.
Translated Text:
Not scanned any codes in the last 30 seconds, reopen Scan tab when you are ready to scan.

Keeping the camera on for long may drain battery.
Opening the Activity tab.

Term: SEQR is designed to scan and read all kinds of QR Codes and identify unsafe content that you may come across. It performs several checks in addition to using information from various online sources to identify potential security risks. It enables you to make informed decisions about whether or not to trust the codes and content.
Translated Text: SEQR is designed to scan and read all kinds of QR Codes and identify unsafe content that you may come across. It performs several checks in addition to using information from various online sources to identify potential security risks. It enables you to make informed decisions about whether or not to trust the codes and content.

Translated Text: The code you scanned contains the following detail

Term: Information you send or receive through the site is secure. Even if the site is flagged safe, always be careful when sharing private information. Look at the address bar to make sure you are on the site you want to visit.
Translated Text: Information you send or receive through the site is secure. Even if the site is flagged safe, always be careful when sharing private information. Look at the address bar to make sure you are on the site you want to visit.

Term: This site has been flagged as unsafe. Visiting this site could trick you into doing something dangerous like installing software or revealing your personal information (for example, passwords, phone numbers, or credit cards) or use your device to do things that you do not intend.
Translated Text: This site has been flagged as unsafe. Visiting this site could trick you into doing something dangerous like installing software or revealing your personal information (for example, passwords, phone numbers, or credit cards) or use your device to do things that you do not intend.

Term: This site does not provide a secure connection. Someone might be able to see or change the information you send and receive through this site. We suggest you do not enter any private or personal information on this page. If possible, do not use the site.
Translated Text: This site does not provide a secure connection. Someone might be able to see or change the information you send and receive through this site. We suggest you do not enter any private or personal information on this page. If possible, do not use the site.

Term: We can't seem to reach the web site. This page doesn't exist or some other horrible error has occurred.
Translated Text: We can't seem to reach the web site. This page doesn't exist or some other horrible error has occurred.

Term: We're working on getting this fixed as soon as we can. Please try again later.
Translated Text: We're working on getting this fixed as soon as we can. Please try again later.

Term: No Internet Connection. Check your network settings and try again.
